            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/369_step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop the <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> in half</p><p>Add them to a baking tray (use <strong>tin foil</strong> to avoid mess!)</p><p>Pat the<strong> basa fillets</strong> dry with <strong>kitchen paper</strong> and place them on the same tray</p><p>Drizzle everything with<strong> olive oil</strong> and season generously with <strong>salt</strong> and<strong> pepper</strong></p><p>Season the <strong>halved</strong> <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> with a pinch of<strong> sugar</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/369_step-5-x200.jpg",
