          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Put the tray in the oven for 12-15 min until the fish is cooked</p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked when it turns opaque and flakes easily</p><p>Meanwhile, chop the<strong> basil</strong> finely,<strong> </strong>including the stalks</p>",
      "order": 6,
