      "instruction": "<p>Chop the<strong> capers</strong> and <strong>black olives</strong> together finely</p><p>Combine both with the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Add 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> – this is your <strong>tapenade</strong></p>",
